1.0.0.name: wordpress/woocommerce-custom-price-label
1.0.0.description:
This plugin extends the WooCommerce e-commerce plugin by allowing to create custom price labels for products (like 'Call for Price' etc.).

This plugin was tested with WooCommerce 2.0.7.

Feedback

  • We are open to your suggestions and feedback - Thank you for using or trying out one of our plugins!
  • Drop us a line at http://www.algoritmika.com
